<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Inertia-v1 blog – Hextra 主题问题修复</title><link>/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/</link><description>Recent content in Hextra 主题问题修复 on Inertia-v1 blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>页面切换时布局偏移修复</title><link>/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E6%97%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%81%8F%E7%A7%BB%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E6%97%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%81%8F%E7%A7%BB%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/</guid><description>
&lt;h2&gt;现象&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="现象"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#%e7%8e%b0%e8%b1%a1" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="此章节的永久链接"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在文档页间切换时，内容区域整体左移/右移跳动。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;原因&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="原因"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="此章节的永久链接"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;内容短的页面无滚动条，内容长的页面出现滚动条（约 15px），导致 &lt;code&gt;clientWidth&lt;/code&gt; 变化，页面布局偏移。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;修复&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="修复"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#%e4%bf%ae%e5%a4%8d" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="此章节的永久链接"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在 &lt;code&gt;assets/css/custom.css&lt;/code&gt; 中添加：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-css" data-lang="css"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;html&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;overflow-y&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;scroll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0"&gt;
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="复制代码"
aria-label="复制代码"
data-copied-label="已复制！"
&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;滚动条始终占位，页面宽度恒定。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>AI自配置的错误</title><link>/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/ai%E8%87%AA%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/hextra-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/ai%E8%87%AA%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</guid><description>
&lt;p&gt;记录因 AI 配置不当导致的问题及修复方案。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>